name: Elisha Cuthbert
description:
Actress

the training was on a model - CyberRealistic 2.0.

I'm Render on - EndlessReality

  • if you want to get speed, drive a sports car

  • if you want to drive off-road, take an SUV

  • if you want to hammer a nail, take a hammer

  • it's the same here - if you want to get results, read the recommendations and follow them

I do not recommend using my LoRA with model RealisticVision

personally, I most often perform generation with parameters: DPM ++ 2M Karras, Sampling Steps 35, Denoising strength 0.35, CFG Scale 3.5-4.5

evaluation of the model is welcome
